title: How Depression Created "LaurDIY" and My YouTube Career
description:
Lauren recounts her struggle with depression and explains how anxiety became the precursor to her career as a YouTuber. The couple reflects on how conflicts including art school rejection, initial anxiety attacks, and past relationships shaped her journey to success.
